#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/addon:2
msgid "Hebrew Tribe"
msgstr "Hebräers-Volk"

#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/addon:3
msgid ""
"Adds the Hebrew tribe (Stamm der Hebräer) to Widelands. Features a unique "
"economy based on clay, branches, and cloth with copper instead of iron."
msgstr ""
"Föögt dat Hebräers-Volk to Widelands hento. 't hett eene eenzigaardige "
"Weertskupp mit Lehm, Twiegen un Stoff mit Koper in Stee vun Iesen."

