msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "First Book of Kings"
msgstr "Erstes Buch der Könige"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew warehouse: Port
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:953
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Serves as a base for overseas colonization and trade. Also stores your "
"soldiers, wares and tools."
msgstr ""
"Deent tum Begünnen vun Hannel un Söken över Seefahrt. Brengt ok diene Lüü un "
"Soldaten unner un verwahrt diene Waren un anner Kraam."

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Hebrew warehouse: Port
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:955
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Similar to the Headquarters a Port can be attacked and destroyed by an "
"enemy. It is recommendable to send soldiers to defend it."
msgstr ""
"As ok dat Raadhuus, kann eene Muu vun Feinden angriepen un verneelt worden. "
"Schick beter Soldatsken, um se to verteidigen."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Branch Collector's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:964
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"'For there is hope for a tree, if it be cut down, that it will sprout again, "
"and that its shoots will not cease.'"
msgstr ""
"»För dor is Hoffn för en Baum, wenn he afsnit weer, dat he wieder trecken "
"schüllt, un dat sien Triebe nich aufhören.«"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Branch Collector's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:966
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "Book of Job"
msgstr "Buch Hiob"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Branch Collector's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:968
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Collects fallen branches from trees in the vicinity. The trees are not "
"harmed."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Note helptext for a Hebrew production site: Branch Collector's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:970
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid ""
"Branches are the primary building material and fuel. The branch collector "
"needs trees nearby."
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Hebrew production site: Fisher's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:977
msgctxt "hebrews_building"
msgid "'Cast your net on the right side of the boat and you will find some.'"
msgstr "»Werf dien Netz an de rechte Slut von de Boot un du wirst wat fannen.«"

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Hebrew production site: Fisher's Hut
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:979
