msgstr "»Un se nähen Feigenblätter an'nanner un maken sik Leibbinden.«"

#. TRANSLATORS: Purpose helptext for a Hebrew production site: Dressmakery
#: addons/hebrews_tribe.wad/tribes/hebrews/units.lua:1155
